You're not going believe this shit.

Like what I do and want to support me so that I can get actual presents this year? https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345

comments.text: Sorry your Christmas haul wasn't a good one Tamers.
comments.author: @pitshoster401

comments.text:
To be a SU fan is to adapt, or so I've learned from watching the show so much. Hell, you should know this, Tamers12345, being the one and only ultimate fan and all. You, after all, have continued to adapt by making what I (and any other sane individual) would consider to be the only thing to rival it and properly continue its legacy (Ian Flynn had the right idea by opting not to write that one-off special, that honor goes to you!). There sadly isn't very much material to delve into, so that's why fans need to adapt to get more out of my personal favorite Sonic continuity. That's the reason for why I'm asking you now to try to adapt and put the baked beans on top of a hotdog. You can always go back to regular Sonic-salivatin' chilidogs, but just once, please, eat a fuckin' BEANDOG. Maybe you'll like it, who knows.

BTW, sorry your mom didn't deliver the SU goods this year. There's always the next, I guess!
